task.summary: Added CHANGES file summarizing versions 0.1 and 0.2
Added first example usage for a regression

Added option to have a temporary run directory for SISSO by setting run_dir = None. This is especially useful when using cross-validation and/or hyperparameters optimization through scikit-learn's GridSearch, RandomSearch, ...
Added unit test for model persistence. Added example usage of model persistence.
Removed @property to input_string (changed unit test accordingly). Adding type checking using mypy: - Added mypy to pyproject.toml - Added pre-commit hook for mypy - Fixed type checking in all files
Fixed but in outputs.py (introduced bug while fixing type hints) Removed print statement in test_outputs
Enabled branch coverage Added coverage requirement of 100 Fixed small bug in nsample setter of SISSODat Added nsample argument to from_dat_file classmethod Added tests for branch coverage
Modified the spelling of "Licence" to "License" everywhere. Adding main page (index.rst) for documentation in docs_rst.
